data.description: Welcome to this stunning old Louisville home boasting large open rooms flooded with an abundance of natural light, accentuating the original hardwood floors and preserving the elegance of the original woodwork. Enjoy the convenience of off-street parking and envision the possibilities of the spacious attic, primed for conversion into additional living space. Delight in the comfort of a full bath on the second floor and a conveniently located half bath on the first floor.
